des:
Ask Alexa to check the latest price of NFTs, including:

- Bored Ape Yacht Club 
- Mutant Ape Yacht club 
- Bored Ape Kennel Club 
- Doodles 
- CryptoMories
- Cool Cats 
- Meebits 
- Gutter Cat Gang 
- Lazy Lions 

Disclaimer: Prices are compared against the latest Ethereum prices, sourcing data from the OpenSea Market book. Ticker/stock quotes are accurate to the minute.
